Name: Average time from \Request Payment\ to \Payment Handled\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Request Payment' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total time from \Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE\ to \Payment Handled\
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time for \Payment Handled\ after \Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total resolution time of \Payment Handled\
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Payment Handled and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ to \Payment Handled\
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time for \Payment Handled\ grouped by \org:resource\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Payment Handled' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:resource

Name: Total time for \Payment Handled\ in cases where \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ occurred
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Payment Handled' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER occurs

Name: Minimum time for \Payment Handled\ in cases without \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Payment Handled and the end of the case

Name: Average time from \Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER\ to \Payment Handled\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total time from \Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER\ to \Payment Handled\ in cases leading to \Payment Handled\
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time it takes \Payment Handled\ after \Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total time it takes \Payment Handled\ after \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum resolution time of \Payment Handled\ in cases with \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Payment Handled and the end of the case

Name: Average time from \Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE\ to \Payment Handled\ in cases with \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total time from \Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE\ to \Payment Handled\ in cases without \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'
